new in v0.3

Core:
	- added backup feature to mysqli driver
	
New form wizard:
	- Some short tag replaced width standard php sintax
	- Multidatabase feature added for datagrids
	- Pagination included by default in datagrids
	
Dbmanager:
	- Now its posible to switch between predefined databases
	- Bugfixing in edit/delete record when the table has not any index defined 
	- It does not set/read project/database from session anymore. Now its posible to have project independent tabs/windows opened in browser 
	- Bugfixing in sql tab
	- Pagination improved

Other:
	- minor bugs fixed

